{"word":"G3980 - πειθαρχέω - peitharchéō - pi-tharkh-eh'-o - Hearken","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πειθαρχέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">peitharchéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pi-tharkh-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hearken</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கீழ்ப்படி, சொல்லைக்கேள்"},{"paragraph":"to obey"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3982 - πείθω - peíthō - pi'-tho/3982\">G3982</a> and <a href=\"#/G757 - ἄρχω - árchō - ar'-kho/757\">G757</a>; to <i>be persuaded</i> by a <i>ruler</i>, that is, (generally) to <i>submit</i> to authority; by analogy to <i>conform</i> to advice: - hearken, obey (magistrates).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3980/3980\">G3980</a>, <a href=\"#/G3981/3981\">G3981</a>, <a href=\"#/G3982/3982\">G3982</a>, <a href=\"#/G3988/3988\">G3988</a>, <a href=\"#/G4006/4006\">G4006</a>, <a href=\"#/G543/543\">G543</a>, <a href=\"#/G544/544\">G544</a>, <a href=\"#/G545/545\">G545</a>"}]}